name: Don't Burn Capital
description: Faith Over Fiat. Don’t Burn Capital. Protect it. $DBC is launched on Cooking.City. $DBC isn’t just a memecoin, it can be a stealth Jump stress test, a conviction mechanic prototype for Meteora, a memetic trojan horse to gauge behavioral liquidity across Solana. $DBC is a conviction test wrapped in fire. A launch built for the ones who hold longer, think sharper, and know that the market doesn’t reward speed it rewards belief.
